FULL-TIME RESULT (1X2)

Two-way bet regarding whether

the total number of goals scored

will be more than the one

quoted or less. In most cases,

the bet appears to exceed or

even be less than 2.5 goals and

two possible outcomes.

Chelsea Arsenal

