Over 3.5 goals              2.80           

GOALS (UNDER/OVER)

Under these types of football

bets, one has to predict the

correct score within the normal

90 minutes of football action.

The odds tend to be quite high

because of the fact that there

are many possible outcomes.

Inter AC Milan

