3 What is Goal Bonanza

Game essentials

Players will have between 150 and 200 football games available for betting on weekly basis.

Football games from all major national and international competitions will be available for betting.

Multiple 3rd party API services will be used to feed available competitions, game schedules and game scores

to ensure data quality and integrity via multi-tier data validation system.

Football games from selected competitions will open for betting with 100 GOAL tokens Goal Bonanza 

sponsored bounty, 24h prior to match start. Bets will be accepted until the start of the football match.

Minimum accepted bet will be 1 GOAL token valued at 0.0002 ETH per 1 GOAL token on launch date. Players 

can wager a minimum of 1 GOAL token on at least 1 of  the 10 available outcomes.

The game pot will be shared between players that successfully predicted the game outcome. In event of no 

winning bets, the pot is thrown in a jackpot game organized every month for players with account level 5 only.

Goal Bonanza will withhold 9.75% retainer from every football game pot as the games organizer.

Withdrawals will be available only for players with account level 3 or above. Users will have to have an ERC20 

compatible token wallet to make a withdrawal. Players collecting winnings by selling tokens on an exchange.

Players will be able to earn 10 tokens for every referred player that will reaches account level 3 via the referral 

program. The referral program will be available when user unlocks account level 2.

Players will be able to earn win additional tokens as a reward for completing various achievements, challenges 

and milestones. Withdrawals of reward tokens will be available only for players with account level 4 or above.

Goal Bonanza doesn’t require any identity verification, submission of forms of identification, credit card and 

bank account details. Players in Goal Bonanza are anonymous and personal data privacy is guaranteed.

