Goal Bonanza smart contract
Goal Bonanza users will interact with a front end interface written in Javascript that creates a smart contract

through the Web3 protocol. The smart contract defines the mechanics of the game such as total number of

users that participate in a single game, wagered tokens per outcome, distribution of winnings, fulfillment of

achievements, distribution of bonuses and rewards, and other rules and restrictions. This front end will

provide general information about the game as well as the most up-to-date scores of the football team that

are competing at any given time.



