How Goal Bonanza platform interacts with the environment
Goal Bonanza will sell the retained tokens from the ICO, which will in later stages be also supplemented by

purchases in the secondary market to refill the funds and ensure liquidity as the user base and turnover of

GOAL tokens in the platform grows. We will be a constant buyer of GOAL tokens in the secondary market.

This will ensure platform liquidity and maintenance of GOAL token funds required for the rewards system

give always and for selling to players.



