Overview of the token environment and flow
The Goal Bonanza Tokens (GOAL) are ERC20 compatible tokens that can be easily transferred or sold

among users of ETH, using standard methods. Moreover, the Goal Bonanza team is in contact with major

exchanges to list GOAL tokens on multiple exchanges shortly after the initial sale ends. GOAL tokens will be

acquired directly on the Goal Bonanza platform via the rewarding system, during the initial sale, or bought on

exchanges in the secondary market.



4 Business model

Our business model is very simple. Effective acquisition of new players, retention and conversion to

paying accounts in order to unlock withdrawal capability and strong stimulation for frequent betting via

gamification methods. The higher the tokens turnover frequency is, the higher the total retainer will be

as percentage from total tokens in circulation in the platform.

